## Tips and steps for successful testing

- Work on the ggrosario-testing data base (must be empty)

- in pom.xml set to true the value of the 
```
<skipTests></skipTests>
```
configuration to skip unit test and be able to initialize the system for the first time.

- Turn off Glassfish server

- Clean the project

- Turn on Glassfish server

- Initialize the system

- Stop Glassfish server

- in pom.xml set to **false** the value of the 

```
<skipTests></skipTests>
```

configuration to skip unit test and be able to initialize the system for the first time.

- Start Glassfish server again

- Feel free to run just the UnitTests or the entrie project and test!
